        "endTime": 13514,
        "slowStartTime": 16540,
        "slowEndTime": 20496
    },
    {
        "text": "First, I crack the egg on the side of a bowl or on a cutting board...",
        "startTime": 14144,
        "endTime": 20324,
        "slowStartTime": 21366,
        "slowEndTime": 30711
    },
    {
        "text": "...and I separate with my thumbs into two shells.",
