        "endTime": 25474,
        "slowStartTime": 31937,
        "slowEndTime": 38436
    },
    {
        "text": "Of course, I have a bowl below and the egg white falls into it.",
        "startTime": 26437,
        "endTime": 29851,
        "slowStartTime": 39805,
        "slowEndTime": 45002
    },
    {
        "text": "Go back and forth until everything is separated.",
        "startTime": 30779,
        "endTime": 33232,
        "slowStartTime": 46318,
        "slowEndTime": 50073
    },
    {
        "text": "In case you get a little egg shell, either in the white or the yolk,...",
        "startTime": 33841,
        "endTime": 36775,
        "slowStartTime": 50912,
        "slowEndTime": 55387
    },
    {
        "text": "...you can separate it with a spoon...",
        "startTime": 37225,
        "endTime": 39567,
        "slowStartTime": 55987,
        "slowEndTime": 59576
    },
    {
        "text": "...or you can let them sit for a while, especially in the egg whites...",
        "startTime": 40249,
        "endTime": 43975,
        "slowStartTime": 60524,
        "slowEndTime": 66187
